### List orders
GET {{host}}/api/v1/orders
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Get order by ID
GET {{host}}/api/v1/orders/{{transaction_id}}
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Fund escrow
POST {{host}}/api/v1/orders/{{transaction_id}}/fund
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "return_url": "http://localhost:5173/dashboard/orders"
}

### Mark delivered
POST {{host}}/api/v1/orders/{{transaction_id}}/deliver
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delivery_proof": "https://example.com/data/output.json",
  "message": "Delivered as requested"
}

### Confirm delivery
POST {{host}}/api/v1/orders/{{transaction_id}}/confirm
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Submit rating
POST {{host}}/api/v1/orders/{{transaction_id}}/rating
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "score": 5,
  "message": "Excellent service"
}

### Get ratings
GET {{host}}/api/v1/orders/{{transaction_id}}/ratings
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Dispute order
POST {{host}}/api/v1/orders/{{transaction_id}}/dispute
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Did not receive deliverable"
}

### List transactions (alias)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/transactions
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}

### Get transaction by ID (alias)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/transactions/{{transaction_id}}
X-API-Key: {{api_key}}
